{"id": "1452934877497393235", "channel_id": "1452934877497393235", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "「一个一个又一个……在无人知晓的浓雾里，我尽情发泄♪」\n「敲开你的脑壳，深入你的大脑，让我们在追逐中打发时间♪」\n\n呼，今天最有意思的事情发生了——战斗！\n🪓蜡像小人：手感黏腻，要速战速决；\n🪓修▼▼脓疱：离远一点打，小心溅一身脓液；\n🪓蹈海者：海腥味过重，最好戴上防毒面罩；\n🪓……实战情报积累中……\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\n***\"One after another... In the mist where no one knows, I vent to my heart's content♪\"\n\"Crack open your skull, poke around your brain; let's play tag until you go insane♪\"***\n\nWhew! The most interesting thing happened today—**BATTLE!**\n🪓Wax Sculptures: Ugh, so sticky to the touch! Must finish 'em quick.\n🪓Sho▼g▼th Pustules: Attack from a distance! Watch out for the pus splatter.\n🪓Seafarers: They STINK!! Better wear a gas mask.\n🪓...Combat intel accumulating...\n\n<@&1440553558238953482>", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T08:04:29.020000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-23T08:20:21.729000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Showoff", "emoji_id": "1400771654199541850", "count": 9}, {"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1400771650064089112", "count": 4}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "Cheerup", "emoji_id": "1400771555939844149", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1452934878906683503", "filename": "2_2-cn.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 7500888, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452934877497393235/1452934878906683503/2_2-cn.jpg?ex=69ccd18d&is=69cb800d&hm=02c2704edc4f7b3068346bf5033cc21d056b943e1d03b08922429db410e68f67&"}, {"id": "1452934880177553450", "filename": "2_2-en.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 7602124, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452934877497393235/1452934880177553450/2_2-en.jpg?ex=69ccd18d&is=69cb800d&hm=cc5bfc124d7263dd50831b9e19c382cf48bf3573a4e450930b3986771c478dc2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "